{"tid":2040814,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[藍屍] 莊思敏FB晒克警書 火速刪Post轉去微博圍爐","createTime":"2020-05-28T23:30:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T02:34:21.000Z","uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7b2eef0a34d9b0e9bd522834c1045b1b7717146a","tid":2040814,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T23:30:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3Wtcuaq_Xad57VtV3-YT4yL51u4=/412x309/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ATQRBR32BILGM7HFQWX33QD6KE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3Wtcuaq_Xad57VtV3-YT4yL51u4%3D%2F412x309%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FATQRBR32BILGM7HFQWX33QD6KE.jpg&h=0cb11e13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n莊思敏和姚瑩瑩去年都有份去警總送暖，被指是「撐警之星」，她們不約而同在社交網上載與警察公共關係科總警司的謝振中合照，不過莊思敏在facebook的Post疑惹來不少網民聲討警暴問題，令她不足兩小時便刪掉，轉為在微博post相，跟小粉紅們圍爐取暖。"},{"pid":"14659117fba89680e01075fe420a08aadf191c98","tid":2040814,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T23:30:50.000Z","msg":"莊思敏留言：「感恩香港有香港警察。感激你們盡全力去守護香港這座城市。你們每一位的付出我們都心存感激。多謝你們。加油。多謝一哥，多謝謝Sir。」還打上「香港警察」、「忠誠勇毅心系社會」的hashtag。就合照所見，二人一同拿着一本名為《守城》的書，露出笑容燦爛。該書封面上印有一班「忠勇毅」full gear列隊的相片，而包裝紙上則寫着「撕裂七百萬人的政治風波」。據悉此書為限量珍藏版，市面上暫時未見有售，不過說到該書最最最珍貴的地方，相信是有謝Sir加持的親筆簽名，難怪莊思敏要「晒命」展示一番。不少「藍忠」都留言讚好，但亦有無數反對聲音，指責警暴問題嚴重，為何還要撐？事後莊思敏刪post，轉為貼出真。愛犬照，指自己教狗狗笑：「我在教他笑，他叫HaHa，所以我不停叫Haha笑。」"},{"pid":"3f91f96c8b8546a42c2eefa765ba70dd4b26cb68","tid":2040814,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T23:31:04.000Z","msg":"另外在謝振中的facebook專頁上，亦有上載謝Sir快人一步，率先拿到該書的照片，在專頁的帖文中更提到指有人用謊言抹黑警隊，又指書內的圖片是紀錄過去一年的風波：「為歷史留下一個真實的印記，為警隊還一個公道。小編有幸先睹為快，閱畢全書，眼淚不禁奪眶而出，因為每一張圖片都見證著警隊『上下一心』、『忍辱負重』。」"},{"pid":"6e84f95593c8090f9bbe36e963781cae3bb4e02b","tid":2040814,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T23:31:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/8Uup-STA_Tt1tbLQVL6GlJcUIzY=/412x309/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HTHHRWSDITJD2YO6TMNNRNU5RA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F8Uup-STA_Tt1tbLQVL6GlJcUIzY%3D%2F412x309%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHTHHRWSDITJD2YO6TMNNRNU5RA.jpg&h=d19f35ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n謝振中親筆簽名"},{"pid":"e748752ccf7a19923e3125119f767b618ada6cb8","tid":2040814,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T23:31:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/zS-v2eK2gmJ0mZFwzE0ZTAKU3hA=/412x498/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HROTPTWWA2YA4XYDJGRVEBRIU4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FzS-v2eK2gmJ0mZFwzE0ZTAKU3hA%3D%2F412x498%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHROTPTWWA2YA4XYDJGRVEBRIU4.jpg&h=cddbbbfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n莊思敏突然刪post，轉貼愛犬haha笑相。"},{"pid":"a68709b86fe9391b826fe1bde9f2495a4ab1740b","tid":2040814,"uid":125168,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T23:33:57.000Z","msg":"又要撐又要縮真係最撚7<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03b0ac8d0f5b264fca5136f12749666b53c1ffc5","tid":2040814,"uid":286897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T23:35:28.000Z","msg":"現代 毛澤東選<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />集<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0XH1RUJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0XH1RUJ.jpg&h=4f13cdcb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"88766a1a9a1cb9f17009269b9c584b6b1ad101cf","tid":2040814,"uid":318505,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e748752ccf7a19923e3125119f767b618ada6cb8","tid":2040814,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T23:31:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/zS-v2eK2gmJ0mZFwzE0ZTAKU3hA=/412x498/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HROTPTWWA2YA4XYDJGRVEBRIU4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FzS-v2eK2gmJ0mZFwzE0ZTAKU3hA%3D%2F412x498%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHROTPTWWA2YA4XYDJGRVEBRIU4.jpg&h=cddbbbfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n莊思敏突然刪post，轉貼愛犬haha笑相。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T23:41:02.000Z","msg":"咁都post出街，話比人知自己弱智？<br />\n雖然藍屍又真係冇撚腦<br />\nAnyway，刪完狗相貼狗相，耐人尋味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b7aa3795fe733fffee806057f540b24a0c118e9","tid":2040814,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T00:09:37.000Z","msg":"警天使？"},{"pid":"ed207a62cc341722af9146c6acff21b578238949","tid":2040814,"uid":211461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T00:14:58.000Z","msg":"搵晒警暴啲相<br />\n屈斷人手腳 yellow object啲嘢<br />\n本書厚過你100倍"},{"pid":"1f73b44d67c5d619e1e99529a1c95399ac33d131","tid":2040814,"uid":38518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2b7aa3795fe733fffee806057f540b24a0c118e9","tid":2040814,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T00:09:37.000Z","msg":"警天使？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T00:29:45.000Z","msg":"劣食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />叫霸王雞好過啦"},{"pid":"7d6c33cc9c9c532a2d25f0752fdbd41f1193020c","tid":2040814,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T00:30:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fc391b582547f45309f3b1a1a7bdb16c851b8ee","tid":2040814,"uid":10757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T00:52:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"